  "system": {
    "description": "<p>A buttstroke is not a melee weapon in the traditional sense, rather using the butt of a longarm to strike a target. While buttstroking is an improvised weapon, it does not incur the penalties for being one, nor will it break if used as a weapon. All weapons with a fixed stock can be used to buttstroke. If a character provokes an AoO on a character wielding a longarm that can buttstroke, that character can use the buttstroke to perform their AoO. A buttstroke can not be upgraded with any melee upgrades.</p>",
